data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! Beautiful Home in Santa Rosa Beach! Just minutes to the Emerald Coast's Sugar Sand Beaches and seconds from the Bay area that has Boat Ramps for the Boat Lovers. 3 Bed 2 Bath with over 1600 Square Feet of Living Space. Spacious Island Style Kitchen with New Appliances. Split Floor Plan. Beautiful Laminated Wood and Tile Flooring throughout. Trey Ceilings in Living Room, Family Room and Primary Bedroom. Primary Bath has Garden Tub, a Walk in Shower and Large Walk-in Closet. New duct work and protective fencing under house, new blower motor in A/C. Large Front and Back Porches. Beautiful Lawn with a Storage Large Building. Vacation Rentals Allowed
